We talking about file browser, multimedia / audio streaming platform.

$ mmplat --dir ./ --filetypes mp4,mp3,pdf

Functionality:
	- list files
		- sort by: type, name
		- search field
	- two clients: JSON, HTTP. one api.
	- stream multimedia type: app/mmpeg, app/mp3 etc
- represt dir as tree w/ metadata
	- return resource identificator specific to the representation
- handler for each node type: 
	-> dir - return list
	-> MM - stream
- handler for media streaming with bytes offset
